   <refsect2info>
    <date>1998-09-21</date>
   </refsect2info>
   <title>
    SQL3
   </title>
   <para>
   <command>CREATE TYPE</command> is an <acronym>SQL3</acronym> statement.
   </para>
  </refsect2>
 </refsect1>
